data.description:
Tucked away outside of town sits this beautiful, updated home on 1.45 acres. The large yard features a brand-new hot tub installed fall of 2022, split rail fence, RV parking and a gorgeous side patio and firepit area that was just poured in the summer of 2021. Inside the stunning home, the sellers have thought of every detail of design with modern farmhouse as their inspiration. From the shiplap accents over the fireplace, dining room wall and bathroom to the updated light fixtures. In the upstairs living room, you will find the perfect window nook that is the best spot to sip your morning coffee and soak in the view. Sellers installed new carpet in fall of 2022. You are going to love this home, from the cozy inside to the ample amount of outdoor space to play and store your all your Montana toys. Call Brittany Buckallew at 406.212.8566 or your real estate professional today. *One of the sellers is a licensed Realtor. Updates to the home include the following:
- Driveway sealed coated - Summer of 2023
- New hot tub - Fall of 2022.
- New carpet in two upstairs bedrooms and stairs - Fall of 2022.
- New paint in upstairs living room, dining room, kitchen and back deck - Spring of 2022.
- New front stamped concrete patio - Summer of 2021.
- Additional parking added and poured - Summer of 2021
- New upstairs bathroom - 2021.
- Kitchen cabinets painted - 2021.
